    <summary>EU Cookie Compliance is an extension which will present the user with the new Cookie notification banner. </summary>
    <description>This extension will automatically show a clear but unintrusive message to your customers regarding the new EU Cookie legislation. Many large customers are adopting the policy that they will not automatically deactivate cookies, but instead they show a notice 'assuming that you are happy' that cookies are active unless you manually turn them off in your browser.&#xD;
&#xD;
Also included is the ability to link the 'More Info' link through to your existing page. All text can be translated easily with inline translation. </description>
